            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Sophie, do you remember what today was?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh? What was it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "...You realize there's a prayer every week at church, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Oh, now that you mention it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "*Sigh*... Right, you hardly ever come."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "When I'm concentrating on Synthesis, I always lose track of what time it is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "...I know. In that case, we should go together next week for prayer."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "What? I don't really want to."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "No, you haven't been coming at all lately. You need to go at least once in a while, and show me you're serious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Understand?"
